Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.03,0:00:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老婆被上了  没想到她是这么淫乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.61,0:00:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚四年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.74,0:00:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在还是不会爰爰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.68,0:00:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了满足我的欲求  就在网络上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.82,0:00:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有所勾结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.33,0:00:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  也不能说跟对方有所了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.31,0:00:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从被别人看到我们的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.05,0:00:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间就有变化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啊  为啥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.69,0:01:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  要打电活给水电工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.04,0:01:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是水电公司吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.68,0:02:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没有水哎  今天可以来看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.82,0:02:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以马上来吗  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.46,0:02:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会等候的  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.80,0:02:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉突然叫来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.24,0:03:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.89,0:03:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要全部拆掉看看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.33,0:03:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家用的是旧款的  可能会花很多时间哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.37,0:03:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.11,0:03:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我开工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.31,0:03:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去客厅了  有事跟我说哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天请回吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公在嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.03,0:04:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有水电工在修东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.04,0:04:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正很快就好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.11,0:04:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是水电工  很快就搞定了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没同题啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.81,0:05:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能这样哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.17,0:05:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别介意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.33,0:08:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.76,0:08:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  认真一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.90,0:09:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别介意他啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.54,0:09:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么旧没办法啦  应该要换新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.32,0:09:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟太太讨论一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.53,0:10:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.04,0:10:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.96,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.67,0:11:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要先说哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.32,0:12:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.30,0:12:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太啊  你家的太旧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.67,0:12:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要换新的才能修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.68,0:12:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太  有沾到东西哦～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.16,0:12:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.81,0:13:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做料理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.05,0:13:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实啊  太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.95,0:13:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心也拍下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.24,0:13:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以保密吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.54,0:13:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.68,0:13:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.89,0:13:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么爱玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.03,0:13:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这老公不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.47,0:14:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  请保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.31,0:14:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我没立场插嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.09,0:14:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟他们是有点交流的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.46,0:14:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也都说你很正
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.17,0:14:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟人正就会引人注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.54,0:14:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好我喝醉就会说溜嘴哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.45,0:14:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.33,0:15:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要拜托我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.74,0:15:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有什么好处吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.05,0:15:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都会做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.69,0:15:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那跟我爱爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.83,0:15:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说都会做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.24,0:15:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那我们去客厅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.82,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.66,0:16:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心  我会保密的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.94,0:16:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太  你知道你在这里很有人气吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.32,0:16:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕  有这么好的太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.32,0:17:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家对太太的胸部很有意见哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝酒后都在讨论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.04,0:18:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么外出找小三呢  不跟老公吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.02,0:18:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多久做一次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.89,0:18:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年以上没做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.53,0:19:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是老公不好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.67,0:19:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉红色的哎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.82,0:19:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以舔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.81,0:21:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟刚刚那位常做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.81,0:22:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.02,0:22:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么色啊  大家都不知道哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.81,0:22:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.63,0:22:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.73,0:22:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.39,0:23:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好猥亵的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.80,0:23:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要来咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.81,0:23:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公都不帮你做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.67,0:24:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要快一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.95,0:24:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.52,0:26:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的屁屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.60,0:26:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看屁眼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.54,0:26:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.61,0:26:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.31,0:26:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看我屁眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.26,0:26:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我来看看咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.32,0:27:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公不去舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.83,0:27:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我来代劳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.80,0:27:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁眼爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.54,0:28:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:05.45,0:28:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁眼很兴奋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.02,0:28:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.16,0:29:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆有这么美丽的屁屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:07.54,0:29:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真猥亵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.82,0:29:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:20.95,0:29:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.75,0:30:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:27.32,0:30:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多汁哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.82,0:31:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要更多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:42.33,0:31:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴很多汁哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:50.67,0:31:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好处理一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:16.16,0:32:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:47.26,0:32:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都硬了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.18,0:33:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:27.80,0:33:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:43.94,0:34:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,细嫩的小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:05.73,0:35:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:34.96,0:35:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要更多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.24,0:36:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:44.73,0:36:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都喷出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:54.66,0:38:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想被干吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.67,0:39:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:03.24,0:39:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真坏心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:53.25,0:40:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以真枪突弹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:09.90,0:41:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:35.45,0:41:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真猥亵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:16.40,0:42:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么肮脏的我可以上吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:22.97,0:42:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:34.54,0:43:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.45,0:43:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.32,0:44:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:37.33,0:45:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:23.31,0:46:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是很大哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:27.68,0:46:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:31.62,0:46:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要嘛  好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:35.62,0:46:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:08.95,0:47:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸡鸡好有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:48.76,0:47:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:55.23,0:47:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:38.94,0:48:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插深一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:18.75,0:49:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:33.90,0:49:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:49.55,0:49:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:50.94,0:50:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:59.05,0:51:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我来代劳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.80,0:51:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又要射了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:20.74,0:51:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:22.53,0:52:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吧  那我先回去咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:30.68,0:52:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次什么时候来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:34.81,0:52:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天下午吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:41.82,0:52:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以早上来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:45.76,0:52:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公不会在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:51.96,0:52:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真色哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:57.67,0:53:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:00.87,0:53:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:02.87,0:53:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我包包里面有名片  等等给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:09.05,0:53:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:13.05,0:53:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:43.68,0:53:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:55.26,0:54:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点来  等你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:33.67,0:54:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:38.87,0:54:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:55.95,0:54:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真色哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:02.53,0:55:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想快点爱爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:11.10,0:55:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:31.69,0:55:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面好湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:22.31,0:56:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想被摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:33.39,0:56:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想被舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:37.02,0:56:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光想像就湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:02.81,0:57:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:20.97,0:57:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:19.46,0:58:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿好猥亵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:40.18,0:58:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:32.60,0:59:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面好湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:24.38,1:01:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:28.02,1:01:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是昨天都没做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:31.82,1:01:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很忙没空  快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:35.82,1:01:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥要我回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:40.30,1:01:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:46.37,1:01:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被发现了吗  还是你有新欢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:53.24,1:01:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么啊  快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:58.45,1:02:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很想爱爱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:05.89,1:02:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说不用管老公吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:09.66,1:02:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:12.66,1:02:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想做哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:14.73,1:02:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:19.73,1:02:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:26.01,1:02:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:51.17,1:02:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢我鸡鸡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:06.58,1:03:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜炊你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:39.95,1:03:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦  快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:45.59,1:03:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啦  够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:13.25,1:04:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:20.09,1:04:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:24.89,1:04:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？  我是水电工
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:28.96,1:04:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  被看到不成体统的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:36.67,1:04:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太太的技木超棒的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:41.81,1:04:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要也来试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:46.51,1:04:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啥啊你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:48.52,1:04:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别介意  水电工也是可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:58.09,1:05:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点帮人家服务
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:30.79,1:05:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以加一个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:33.66,1:05:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:36.10,1:05:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有两根哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:07.66,1:06:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大热天工作真辛苦哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:12.23,1:06:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊  是工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:14.24,1:06:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跑东跑西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:26.65,1:06:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就来修太太家的水管
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:32.32,1:06:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:38.89,1:06:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以跟太太这样做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:45.17,1:06:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安啦  她喜欢鸡鸡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:11.29,1:07:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,技木超好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:22.94,1:07:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人真会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:30.24,1:07:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥啊  要是有时间的话要不要玩一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:41.39,1:07:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这祥啊  好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:49.66,1:07:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:58.01,1:08:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:11.52,1:08:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边  请坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:18.03,1:08:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给小哥看一下小穴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:24.87,1:08:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看美人穴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:31.67,1:08:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么说了  给他看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:43.15,1:08:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:52.29,1:08:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他瞧瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:58.67,1:09:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒  脚也很美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:06.51,1:09:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要更多吗  想直接一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:14.88,1:09:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:27.16,1:09:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞啥啊  小哥上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:34.74,1:09:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:39.01,1:09:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这祥啊  我来咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:55.09,1:09:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥真大胆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:00.09,1:10:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太想看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:04.87,1:10:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别挡住啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:16.08,1:10:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥  觉得如何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:22.88,1:10:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:33.96,1:10:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉红色的哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:40.10,1:10:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天小哥能来太好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:45.74,1:10:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  美人小穴真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:53.38,1:10:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以近一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:06.53,1:11:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥这祥就满意了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:11.67,1:11:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想舔舔想摸摸吗  今天可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:34.59,1:11:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我来咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:55.81,1:12:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥  感觉如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:00.65,1:12:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.10,1:12:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敏感
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:56.74,1:13:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥  我们平常是这样玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:07.52,1:13:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥也想试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:21.10,1:13:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:28.50,1:13:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为了润滑  可以来点口水吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:42.52,1:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真猥亵
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:51.96,1:13:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真猥亵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:54.53,1:13:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:58.87,1:14:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.38,1:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥  一开始请先慢一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:15.02,1:14:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这祥这家伙比较开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:22.89,1:14:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:43.51,1:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥  都放进去咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:13.74,1:15:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何  爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:34.73,1:15:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样比较好插
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:40.60,1:15:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁眼都看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:09.80,1:16:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体态真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:06.81,1:18:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太高潮了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:10.52,1:18:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:30.37,1:18:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:35.38,1:18:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也含我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:41.15,1:18:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:53.23,1:18:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边要上咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:15.38,1:20:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公司啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:19.31,1:20:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:24.82,1:20:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:31.89,1:20:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在有点远哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:37.86,1:20:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要啊  可是有客人哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:46.67,1:20:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:55.08,1:21:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是说不方便啦  是现在要嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:01.52,1:21:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  我懂了  我这去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:17.24,1:21:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公司有事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:20.17,1:21:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:24.88,1:21:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才刚开始爽而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:28.25,1:21:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点抱歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:34.39,1:21:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:38.66,1:21:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥是来修水电的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:42.66,1:21:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  该修水管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:48.30,1:21:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好修喔  一定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:54.68,1:22:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也想继续做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:02.88,1:22:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那抱歉  我会再来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:08.89,1:22:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请好好享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:23.24,1:22:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然他走了  那我去修水管咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:31.81,1:22:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:39.25,1:22:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊  小穴都湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:48.60,1:22:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我来好好为你整修吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:55.50,1:22:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都漏水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:37.44,1:23:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真猥亵哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:23.89,1:24:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:34.30,1:24:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:43.51,1:24:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:49.25,1:24:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:24.25,1:25:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:30.39,1:25:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公很晚才会回来  待着啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:37.16,1:25:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:51.88,1:25:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再干一轮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:57.65,1:26:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:14.43,1:26:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:17.17,1:26:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  我是来修水电的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:28.01,1:26:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:32.15,1:26:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  今天带新品来换
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:38.16,1:26:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:42.03,1:26:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚  还在这么热的天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:47.93,1:26:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公今天真早
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:53.41,1:27:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来要喝酒  但主任生病
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:09.89,1:27:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我现在去拿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:20.53,1:27:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水道看起来还没好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:25.51,1:27:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还在确认有没有零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:35.75,1:27:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望快点弄好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:38.52,1:27:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:43.52,1:27:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:53.87,1:27:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可以修好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:56.87,1:28:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好  如果有零件的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:06.75,1:28:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在等联络啊  真辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:20.09,1:28:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话来了  等我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:26.23,1:28:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:31.50,1:28:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在客人这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:39.65,1:28:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概还要一小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:54.53,1:29:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要花一小时左右啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:04.74,1:29:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:09.38,1:29:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  他啊  不过零件上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:18.38,1:29:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  有联络呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:28.39,1:29:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:36.17,1:29:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我在联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:51.08,1:29:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:55.39,1:30:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样被发现就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:05.17,1:30:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:13.24,1:30:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我会快点把这里结束的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:25.15,1:30:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:29.09,1:30:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:32.23,1:30:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也去处理  先这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:06.89,1:31:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太  这样不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:20.51,1:31:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:55.17,1:32:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的  厨房还没好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:04.88,1:32:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭会很晚才能做好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:14.79,1:32:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以去外面解决吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:19.23,1:32:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:31.14,1:32:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水电工还在  我必须留着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:41.02,1:32:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:46.89,1:32:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是有想吃的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:51.73,1:32:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是昨天说的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:55.60,1:32:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天没特别想吃的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:02.74,1:33:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没气氛啊  想说能喝酒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:11.02,1:33:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果没成
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:14.89,1:33:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是有很多酒肉朋友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:21.73,1:33:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这个时间约也只会被拒绝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:33.87,1:33:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:37.94,1:33:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想说今天就在家里吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:48.52,1:33:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:53.09,1:34:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  辛苦了  现在结束啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:01.17,1:34:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在吗  好哦  反正我也闲着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:12.88,1:34:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打来的正好  我要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:24.02,1:34:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我现在过去咯  待去见
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:33.67,1:34:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:37.94,1:34:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能去晚点回来哦  我懂了  请小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:24.58,1:35:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗  在寝室做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:09.16,1:36:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太  要不要跟我交往啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:18.24,1:36:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙放着不管吧  个性这么差劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:37.65,1:37:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:54.29,1:38:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:00.17,1:39:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:38.00,1:39:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想被舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:18.74,1:40:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太想怎样啊  说说看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:24.15,1:40:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴想被舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:35.73,1:40:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴想被舔  请尽量舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:50.03,1:42:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:55.37,1:42:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:03.14,1:43:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:28.60,1:43:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里想被舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:33.01,1:43:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥要问
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:36.24,1:43:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说就不舔哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:42.25,1:43:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴跟屁眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:19.65,1:45:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:46.00,1:45:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又流汗了  可以舔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:12.52,1:48:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:47.39,1:48:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:03.66,1:50:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想被插入
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:14.07,1:50:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:28.32,1:50:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:52.88,1:50:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:14.17,1:51:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:23.58,1:51:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:25.50,1:52:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插深一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:33.51,1:52:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:47.16,1:52:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:35.67,1:53:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插爆我小穴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:41.88,1:53:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:47.51,1:54:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:17.87,1:56:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以插爆你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:22.67,1:56:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插爆我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:28.01,1:56:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把大鸡鸡放进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:34.45,1:57:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:13.85,1:58:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要射进去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:37.64,1:58:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:42.38,1:58:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全射到我小穴里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:49.52,1:58:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:23.79,1:59:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后每天做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:28.23,1:59:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会等你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:43.68,1:59:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在等你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:49.01,1:59:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后我们每天都有做
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:00.73,2:00:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也跟老公来一发好了
